sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller<br/>Operator
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as Inference Client
    participant Service as Runtime Service<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Puller as Storage Puller<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RuntimeAdapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8001/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Server<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: Model Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply Predictor CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount/kubectl
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event<br/>Predictor created
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Resources created
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over ModelMesh,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Loading
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Register model metadata<br/>Auth: Basic auth (optional)
        etcd-->>ModelMesh: Metadata stored
        ModelMesh->>Puller: Download model request<br/>gRPC/8086
        Puller->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
        S3-->>Puller: Model artifacts
        Puller-->>ModelMesh: Download complete
        ModelMesh->>RuntimeAdapter: Load model command<br/>gRPC/8001
        RuntimeAdapter->>Runtime: Load into runtime<br/>gRPC/8085
        Runtime-->>RuntimeAdapter: Model loaded
        RuntimeAdapter-->>ModelMesh: Load complete
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 3: Inference Request
        Client->>Service: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTP/8008<br/>Auth: None (default)
        Service->>RESTProxy: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8008
        RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: Convert to gRPC<br/>gRPC/8033
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Lookup model location<br/>Auth: Basic auth
        etcd-->>ModelMesh: Pod with loaded model
        ModelMesh->>ModelMesh: Route to target pod<br/>gRPC/8080 internal
        ModelMesh->>Runtime: Execute inference<br/>via Adapter gRPC/8085
        Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Prediction result
        ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
        RESTProxy-->>Service: Convert to HTTP
        Service-->>Client: JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 255)
        Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Runtime: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP/2112
        Runtime-->>Prometheus: Runtime metrics
        Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Auth: mTLS
        Controller-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics
    end
